60
00:05:07,359 --> 00:05:08,359
Kak Qingqing.

61
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,559
Di manakah kuih Osmanthus?

62
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,679
Tak ada.

63
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,679
Tiada kuih Osmanthus, tiada kuih badam,

64
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:14,600
