83
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:50,359
Terima kasih, Tuhan. Kecut hati saya.

84
00:05:50,679 --> 00:05:53,559
Kenapa syaitan naga akan berada
di Kediaman Xiahou?

85
00:05:55,559 --> 00:05:57,640
