selepas awak balik ke gunung?

101
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,839
(Saya akan merindui awak.)

102
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,760
(Rasanya)

103
00:07:56,679 --> 00:07:57,880
(lembut.)

104
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:04,040
Buah berangan gula.

105
