(Apa?)

106
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,160
(Buah berangan gula?)

107
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,640
Apakah ini?

108
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,840
Buah berangan gula!

109
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,280
