110
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,520
Semalam, saya mimpi tentang
buah berangan gula.

111
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,080
Kenapa ia muncul pada hari ini?

112
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,080
